                                               Eshalurd The Left Hand of Armageddon
Starting stats 5 strenght, 5 agility, 10 inteillgence, Stats gain per level, 0.80 Strenght, 0.80 Agility, 1.00 Inteillgence.
Base movespeed 300, Base attack damage 3-9, Base Regeneration Health 0.4, Base Regeneration Mana 0.7.

total base stats at level 40 - 37 Strenght - 37 Agility - 50 Inteillgence -
Doom model

Small Lore -- Brother of Esharad and betrayed of Armageddon the Chaos Lord, Eshalurd now follow his new Chaos Lord Mongrethod as his
fellow commander with Esharad. 

-Note for his 3 basic spells, they will have 7 levels only having 1 level in total, the other levels will give passive stats for him and
buffing those spells slightly. his spells will gain increase damage base on Eshalurd level. Eshalurd will have 15 points to put in his
3 basic spells, his passive and ult will unlock when he reach the level needed. he will gain a level point at level 3 6 9 12 15 18 21
24 27 30 32 34 36 38 40

