SPELL Q Dooming Slash - Physical -
deal high amount of damage to a single target, breaking the target armor to -3 -4 -5 -6 -7 -8 -9 and cannot be increase but can be
lowered. If the target is below 20% health, Dooming Slash will deal increase damage and have no coldown on those target. this spell will
gain 5% increase damage and 3.7% manacost increase for every level of Eshalurd. Also restore some health to Eshalurd base on the damage
and also his max total health. Also increase Eshalurd Strenght and Attack speed for every point spend in Dooming Slash. the debuff armor
lost will last 5 seconds.

