add a new Modifier Seven Hell Strike
Dooming Slash will bounce after striking its target, bouncing 7 time dealing 45% less damage for those 7 strike and they will heal him
as well (only the Health restore Base on DMG) and if it kill the target they Bounce on, reset the number of Bounce to 7 again and
increase the bounce damage by 25% (can proc without limits). Eshalurd will gain 1 stack of Doomed Slash every time it bounce 4 time
and every stacks will increase the base damage of Dooming Slash by 1, at 3 stacks, increase Dooming Slash cast range by 145 and reduce
its mana cost by 25, at 5 stacks, increase Eshalurd attack range by 95 and his attack damage by 27, at 8 stacks, increase the Health
Restore base on Max health by 1.3% and reduce its coldown by 4. Max stacks of 10 and 2 stacks are lost upon losing 17% max health in
one hit and 5 stacks are lost on death.


