Add a new Modifier Infernal Burn
LVL? Death will do 0.1% of the target max health for every 1 levels of Eshalurd and his target on Non-Boss Units and for bosses, every
1 levels of Eshalurd and his target they will lose 0.3 Health regeneration for the same duration of the debuff of LVL? Death. If LVL?
Death kill the target it will Release a Infernal Globe that will give 1 Strenght and 2 Agility upon Pickup for Eshalurd, max of 12 stacks
of Infernal Globe buff and they last until he dies. at 12 stacks of Infernal Globe pickup, LVL? Death will gain 10 base damage and reduce
its mana cost by 75. Also change the damage of LVL? Death to Pure (doesnt need to be at 12 stacks). also make the magic resist lost to
become Pure damage increase.


SPELL E Hells Flames - Physical -
Eshalurd will flame up the ground around him dealing low damage every 0.3 seconds but reducing their Armor by 0.2 for every tick
of damage taken. Eshalurd will also gain 0.2% health regeneration with a base health regeneration as well that with scale on his AGI
and STR. This spell will gain 3.5% increase damage and 1.3% manacost increase for every level of Eshalurd. The armor debuff will last 3.5
seconds after leaving Hells Flames radius. Also increase Eshalurd Inteillgence and Mana Regeneration for every points in Hells Flames

base damage 6+4% of Agility and Strenght
