add a new Modifier Hell Aura
Hells Flames will follow Eshalurd instead of being casted under him and staying here, each time it damage any targets it will gain 6 bonus
radius and 25% chance to also gain 0.4 seconds duration bonus. Hells Flames will also give its bonus regeneration to allys for 50% reduction
of the total regen. If Hells Flames last at least 14 seconds, it will gain 150 bonus radius and 50% increase damage for its remaining
duration. If Hells Flames makes it to 19 seconds duration, Eshalurd will gain 50% damage reduction for the remaining duration. Hells Flames
will stay on Coldown as long its still has duration remaining. Eshalurd will deal 20% extra damage to Non-Bosses units under Hells Flames.
Eshalurd will gain 14 Strenght, Inteillgence and Agility IF Hells Flames last 26 seconds and that buff will last until he dies.


PASSIVE DoomBringer
