and also reducing his 3 basic spell mana cost as well, Eshalurd will gain 11% movespeed for 4.5 seconds after casting a spells or item
effect and also reduce the coldown of items by 10% 15% 20% 25%. Each 15 seconds, Eshalurd next spell will have 12% total mana cost reduce
and have 8% 16% 24% 32% bonus damage (can be toggle on and off).Each stack of health gain will have their own duration of 40 50 60 70
seconds. DoomBringer will be active at level 3 and will upgrade at level 9 17 25.

